readme-edits

My Healthy Cart- An android application

We have created a system in which we are getting input from user in the terms of speech/text on android phone. 
The user enters his/her details which user includes contact and personal details including their allergies and diseases. 
Based on their health condition our system suggests the user the heathly dietery substitues including fruits., vegetables and diary products.
